{"tid":1002142,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"胃酸倒流問題","createTime":"2019-01-30T17:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T04:21:42.000Z","uid":228766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b9a92161c044b51e7a784bc57eb60268515daf2b","tid":1002142,"uid":228766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:09:49.000Z","msg":"胃脹，胃氣多，胃酸倒流，火燒心，食完壓心口好似比野壓住<br />\n食左一個月ppi, 想停藥，但停藥後症狀又返黎<br />\n食野食7成飽，都係會火燒心<br />\n食緊中藥，但效果唔明顯<br />\n有無人係長期胃酸倒流，之後好番?"},{"pid":"ed75a479567d8b24d04e1a0822920d16cc9a869b","tid":1002142,"uid":31254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T18:47:22.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n試下叫份外賣食下"},{"pid":"ce07b71eeea7a1410ee8f97de0a66c2f6e0a13e8","tid":1002142,"uid":87613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T20:14:34.000Z","msg":"驗下係咪幽門菌"},{"pid":"af9b6e577333eb5205390dc6862b30ceab6872e5","tid":1002142,"uid":50677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:20:32.000Z","msg":"有胃酸倒流幾年食過幾隻藥都無效,做左手術半拿無再番發。"},{"pid":"bc03d65bd36c3c174f7259c6c23a2f73afea0143","tid":1002142,"uid":228766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af9b6e577333eb5205390dc6862b30ceab6872e5","tid":1002142,"uid":50677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:20:32.000Z","msg":"有胃酸倒流幾年食過幾隻藥都無效,做左手術半拿無再番發。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:42:05.000Z","msg":"醫生有無話咩原因連食ppi都無效?<br />\n未做手術之前會唔會經常覺得喉嚨有氣頂住?"},{"pid":"bf1fcac9d6de8a1fa9f4b70ad52a617e74c2bdd0","tid":1002142,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:49:05.000Z","msg":"樓主壓力大唔大"},{"pid":"11fa9b3eaa02ecde7d713e7e2301d42489dd5d42","tid":1002142,"uid":228766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf1fcac9d6de8a1fa9f4b70ad52a617e74c2bdd0","tid":1002142,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:49:05.000Z","msg":"樓主壓力大唔大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:52:06.000Z","msg":"一般，不過有時要返通宵，所以可能之